                          <Paragraphs>
                            <Paragraph>
                              <TextRuns>
                                <TextRun>
                                  <Value>       The Department of Engineering will call in the Letter of Credit ten (10) days prior to its expiration date, unless the Department has determined that it will release the Letter of Credit and no extension is required.</Value>
